A fang that appears to always have a shadow cast over it. The only salvageable piece from the cobbled construction of the Ratapult. Shamans use these treated leather bags to hold various reagents for producing their concoctions. Surprisingly high-quality body armor form fit to be worn by only the most physically fit ratmen. The most astonishing thing about this weapon is that a goblin managed to wield it effectively. Sought after by many alchemists and wizards for their potent magical properties. This supernaturally cold substance is believed to be what gives the Yeti an extremely low temperature. Wendigo fangs have been known to be used by northern survivalists as makeshift blades. The central cores of Ice Dragons are said to be the main source of their magic, but does not correlate to any known organ in the dragon species.
