An autobiographical account of a scholar's journey through abandoned temples of unknown deities and the accounts of locals about their origin.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] Interviews about opinions of the afterlife from leading figures in the cults of Krypta, Dauros and Agrela.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An in-depth primer about the most noteworthy monsters known to have existed in Ardania's past.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] Highlights the myriad notable goblin tribes and the complex history of goblins inhabiting civilized lands.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A compilation of recent eyewitness accounts of a strange and ominous cult gaining a foothold in the lowest classes of society.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] The written accounts of an ancients lich's take on the meaning of life and the entropy of existence.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] The written observations of a Monk from the north living in seclusion for three decades to contemplate the nature of the snow that fell regularly in his mountain home.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A retelling of the stories about the common ancestry between humans, dwarves, elves and gnomes.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] Holds more controversial stories and theories of a common ancestor linking dwarves to giants alongside one linking elves to goblins.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] This book tells of the ancestral links between the various races of monsters covering Ardania.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] Writings of the period of time during which Styx and Stones were rampaging across the land, sewing terror and destruction, tearing through both civilized and monstrous races.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] Records about the centennial fervor that overcomes worshippers of Lunord. These events often resulted in mass converts to Lunord.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A novelization of the events revolving around the Scions of Chaos, focusing on the first four generations of Scions.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An uplifting title about Gnomish perseverance and optimism in the face of hardship.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A children's story about a Gnomish Champion wandering from city to city to steal from corrupt officials and using the money for lavish, bombastic parties.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] The title is the only written word, for the book contains nothing but illustrations of battles heavily featuring the Barbarian followers of Krolm.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A collection of the ominous prophecies depicting the legendary two-headed dragon and the destruction foretold to follow in its wake.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] The pieced-together ramblings of the survivors of an adevnturing party said to have ventured through a stretch of wilderness inhabited entirely by Daemonwoods.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An alchemist's writings about the potential uses for Oculus Eyes in potion-making.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An in-depth analysis of the origins of the Lycanthrophic disease responsible for the emergence of Werewolves.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An autobiography of a Paladin recounting her enslavement by Rrongol and her ferocious, bloody escape from the slave pits.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] An ultimately fruitless investigation into the sudden disappearance of Druids from the world and the sharp rise in the violent pushback of servants of nature against civilization.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] The classical story of how Dirgo the Cyclops became blind.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] A bestiary that compiles the habitats and nature of a myriad of dangerous creatures known to hibernate for lengthy periods of time.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color] This book covers the discrepancies, both magical and mundane, in historical accuracy over the course of Ardanian civilization.[color:BCFFBC][newline][newline]Experience: 250[/color][color:DDBB44][newline]Level: 1[/color]
